---
title: Blog
description: The Hybrid Group Blog Entries.
layout: home
page_title: Blog
pageable: true
---
- wrap_layout :layout do
	.blog-content-list
		- page_articles.each_with_index do |article, i|
			%article
				%h2= link_to article.title, article
				%time{:datetime => article.date}= article.date.strftime('%A, %b. %e %Y')
				= article.summary(500)

		%section.pagination
			%div.left
				- if prev_page
					= link_to 'Recent posts', prev_page
			%div.right
				- if next_page
					= link_to 'Previous posts', next_page